    "The embedded sequence } { t h retains the semantic structure of the original features and provides a continuous input basis for subsequent temporal modeling.",
    "To address the uneven time intervals of EHR data, the model designs a learnable time alignment function to adaptively adjust the dependency strength between different time steps."
